locations.intro: Paradiso is on the Weteringschans 6-8 in Amsterdam. That is very close to Leidseplein. From every part of the city there are trams heading towards Leidseplein. locations.title: Paradiso Noord
locations.intro:
Paradiso Noord is on IJpromenade 2. That is very close to Amsterdam Central Station. Just take the free ferry to Buiksloterweg and you will find it on your left hand side. Attending a club night? Then Paradiso Noord has another entrance, situated at Buiksloterweg 5c. That is on the back side of the building.
Wanna have diner close-by? There is a restaurant called THT in the same building as the venue. Be aware you can only pay by card in the whole venue, including the restaurant.
